descriptionNullable:
### Context
This dataset is part of an ongoing project to scrape darkweb market listings from historical sources and eventually expand that to include contemporary listings.

### Content
Title	- Title of listing
Sellerid	- Seller Username
PriceUSD	- Price in US dollars (converted from BTC price using exchange rate of the scrape date)
PriceBTC	- Price in Bitcoin
Rating	- Product rating
Reviews	- Number of customer reviews
Origin	- Country that the product ships from
Destination	- Country or region where the product can be shipped to
Category	- Category of item in marketplace
Subcategory	- Subgroup within Category
Market	- Name of darkweb market
Date - Date that the data was scraped


### Acknowledgements
The data has been extracted from html files made available by Gwern Branwen. I'd recommend checking out his website (https://www.gwern.net/DNM-archives) for more information about the data collection process, access to other market data and an assortment of interesting essays/experiments.


### Notes
As with most darknet market data, a lot of important information is held within poorly formatted listing titles so you'll want to get comfortable with regular expressions in order to extract valuable information.
Rating and Reviews have no values for roughly half of the listings. These features weren't implemented until later versions of the website.
